&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead oversight of a diversified portfolio of 150–200 GP investments across strategies and geographies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop scalable frameworks for portfolio monitoring and performance tracking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with investment teams on quarterly updates and monitoring business plan progress&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Reporting &amp;amp; Analytics&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver institutional-quality investor reporting/deal snapshots/accounting detail on a quarterly basis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and implement next-generation reporting tools, leveraging automation and AI where appropriate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Investor &amp;amp; Stakeholder Communication&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support investor relations efforts with high-quality, timely, and insightful responses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a key liaison between investors and capital markets team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Operational Excellence&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee capital call processes and entity formation for new investments and quarterly replenishments &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and implement technology solutions (including AI-driven tools) to improve workflows and data integrity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Accounting &amp;amp; Structural Fluency&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee partnership-level financial reporting, including capital accounts, distribution calcs, and tax reporting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with accounting and tax teams to ensure accuracy and consistency across the portfolio&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
