&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a dynamic and experienced Senior Project Manager to lead coordination, tracking, and execution across a portfolio of projects and programs associated with the Point of the Mountain master plan including its public (roads, utilities, parking garages, and event venue) and private components (mixed-use residential, retail, and commercial office). The ideal candidate will be a self-starter capable of making an immediate impact, effectively managing vendors, and navigating complex projects, operating as an extension of senior leadership.&lt;/p&gt;
