&lt;li&gt;Oversee and maintain Public Infrastructure District (PID)development budgets and schedules.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a consolidated program-level view of all projects, including schedules, milestones, dependencies, and critical path items.&lt;/li&gt;
